{"tid":1174509,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"神奈川公園19人遇刀襲包括13童 2人心肺停止刀手被捕","createTime":"2019-05-28T01:47:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T01:56:29.000Z","uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1a27c93b4c872a2355949965afd0a498ec23aba5","tid":1174509,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T01:47:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%A5%9E%E5%A5%88%E5%B7%9D%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%9219%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%87%E5%88%80%E8%A5%B2%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC13%E7%AB%A5%E3%80%803%E4%BA%BA%E5%BF%83%E8%82%BA%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E5%88%80%E6%89%8B%E8%A2%AB-004505968.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%25A5%259E%25E5%25A5%2588%25E5%25B7%259D%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%259C%259219%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2581%2587%25E5%2588%2580%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E5%258C%2585%25E6%258B%25AC13%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E3%2580%25803%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25BF%2583%25E8%2582%25BA%25E5%2581%259C%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E5%2588%2580%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%25A2%25AB-004505968.html&d=4a077UaaKOqSfaiyS2iiQZ4O1D3QR3Td9ugMDSJ%2BOB4%3D&h=0b5f2ff6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%A5%9E%E5%A5%88%E5%B7%9D%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%9219%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%87%E5%88%80%E8%A5%B2%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC13%E7%AB%A5%E3%80%803%E4%BA%BA%E5%BF%83%E8%82%BA%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E5%88%80%E6%89%8B%E8%A2%AB-004505968.html</a><br />\n<br />\n日本神奈川縣川崎市周二（28日）有人在公園用利刀刺傷19人，傷者至少包括13名年僅6至7歲的小學女生；其中2人心肺停止。5旬疑兇已經被捕，他疑因自殘而同告心肺停止，警方正在調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n警方稱，當地時間早上7時46分左右接報，有多人在登戶第一公園被人刺傷，警員趕到後將持利器的兇徒制服。1名大人及1名小學女生受傷後心肺停止，另有1名6歲女童及1名4旬女子重傷。疑兇則刺傷了自己的頸部，傷勢嚴重心肺停止；警方在現場發現兩把廚刀。據指，疑兇是突然向等巴士的途人發難施襲，動機未明。<br />\n<br />\n事發公園距離登戶電車站約200米，位於當地住宅區的一隅。而距離事發現場約1.3公里的一所小學的男職員則表示，收到有該校學生受傷的消息，現正進行確認。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/CMyz1G1ZH8ItQwsXSSRK5g--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/4a6bb904a901f4c1856c8949f57aa14f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FCMyz1G1ZH8ItQwsXSSRK5g--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F4a6bb904a901f4c1856c8949f57aa14f&h=7c9cd5bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現場留下大灘血漬。（電視畫面）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d774ddcb34b8161033c3f40467a5b4d2f6a5f901","tid":1174509,"uid":124277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T01:53:46.000Z","msg":"d o靚仔太撚嘈"},{"pid":"8358f4d11d4bb9166cbacfbc86164b1b311b55c3","tid":1174509,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T01:56:29.000Z","msg":"殺小朋友係犯法<br />\n日本人咁有禮貌係唔會咁做"}]}